{"tid":1809613,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"鄭錦滿：收過轉介 但知是本人負責就婉拒 因為私怨放棄幫朋友，咁當初都唔係真係好想幫到個朋友 又話熱血公民唔幫手","createTime":"2020-01-03T08:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T08:51:02.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"047b09cb5ca890e827d4c0f838c224e3b0ca9008","tid":1809613,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1012227302488703&amp;id=100011043274700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1012227302488703%26id%3D100011043274700&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7NjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=32bb32fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1012227302488703&amp;id=100011043274700</a><br />\n轉接收到一個求助，求助人希望我方協助他的朋友，但一知道聯絡人要係本人之後，就婉拒了。<br />\n<br />\n我估計對方聽信網上抹黑，一些不能fact check的謠言，然後作出此決定。<br />\n<br />\n如果你要搵人幫，自己當然可以選擇搵咩人幫忙；但如果我要幫朋友求援，我就會不惜一切，什麼私怨、面子都不重要吧？<br />\n<br />\n如果因為「私怨」而決定放棄幫朋友，咁當初都唔係真係好想幫到個朋友、唔係好想成事啫。<br />\n<br />\n要寫出來，因為以我對那幫人的認知，會調轉槍頭話熱血唔幫手。"},{"pid":"3164cd2e82172290d2a409060b4fe81204345f2a","tid":1809613,"uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:42:18.000Z","msg":"提防熱青城"},{"pid":"32985bbbf8422a2df0aeee8e4af549d41fef2955","tid":1809613,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3164cd2e82172290d2a409060b4fe81204345f2a","tid":1809613,"uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:42:18.000Z","msg":"提防熱青城"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:43:15.000Z","msg":"拉咗先"},{"pid":"aa6c3c5951953f2f219b7c65c3ed632dd549e688","tid":1809613,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:51:02.000Z","msg":"射撚滿你寫呢篇野出黎咪又係私怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最尾個句出賣左你"}]}